00:06.072 --> 00:08.073
<i>that the baby</i>
<i>Corinne is carrying is his.</i>

00:08.074 --> 00:09.074
<i>Eunice and Dutch</i>

00:09.075 --> 00:10.576
<i>are unbelievably happy</i>
<i>on the farm,</i>

00:10.577 --> 00:12.077
<i>although believe it or not,</i>

00:12.078 --> 00:14.580
<i>the police know</i>
<i>where they're hiding.</i>

