<i>Everyone still believes</i>
<i>that Chester is dead,</i>

00:29.095 --> 00:30.095
<i>and Chester believes</i>
<i>he's somebody,</i>

00:30.096 --> 00:33.098
<i>he just can't remember</i>
<i>who that somebody is.</i>

00:33.099 --> 00:34.600
<i>Can't believe it?</i>

00:34.601 --> 00:36.603
<i>You will after</i>
